Subject: [PATCH 39/43] ethtool: implement ETHTOOL_MSG_PHYSID_ACT message

Request physical NIC identification (by blinking a LED), equivalent of
ETHTOOL_PHYS_ID.

Send one notification when blinking starts and one when it ends.

